				I myself am a Necromancer, and have been for a long time. I can beyond a doubt say we are the Best class at Soloing things outside 50+ range. After that.. we are defenseless. Our Dots are resisted by the things with insane saves.. as well as fear and all other things.. in plane raids we are left with a Pet to do our job, and a few spells that hurt somewhat.<BR>
<BR>
As for our summon corpse spell helping with the Clerics job. Its expensive, a cleric can res for free, everything we do of that sort costs us. Be it a Jade Inlaid Coffin or taking out another guy so i could res the other.<BR>
<BR>
A person to person mana transfer would be a good idea as well, for those Raids where we pretty much have to sit down cause the Mob has resisted everything we throw at them, we are left to do nothing but med and watch.<BR>
<BR>
Between the 1-50 range tho, we have no need for ANYTHING. Our class is strong in that range when things dont have a ton of life. I just wish we had some spell later on that could let us hit those Mobs with 100% resist so that we could be effective.<BR>
<BR>
You say in a group we play a good role.. hmm.. Screaming Terror is resisted often, and tends to aggro things. Our Darkness spells turn to crud after Engulfing Darkness, they get resisted alot after that for too much mana to waste.<BR>
<BR>
To the person that spoke of the Ignite/Chill Bone spells, its not too bad really.. it was just ment to be cool, but they shouldnt have put it in like that if it affects other things.<BR>
